 * These are the default line colors, once one is used the next one will be used
 * and then the next one, then the next...
 */

  "hsl(237, 70%, 71%)",
  "hsl(346, 84%, 65%)",
  "hsl(53, 73%, 61%)",
  "hsl(179, 54%, 37%)",
  "hsl(0, 87%, 66%)",
  "hsl(175, 65%, 74%)",
  "hsl(0, 100%, 28%)",
  "hsl(191, 78%, 45%)",
  "hsl(267, 46%, 30%)",
  "hsl(217, 68%, 68%)",
  "hsl(0, 68%, 46%)",
  "hsl(82, 47%, 60%)",
];

export default chartColors;
